caption: Very disappointing, no highlighting of the few beautiful pieces that are in this Heritage House, an accumulation of very uneven things. This is a very respectable approach but there is a serious lack of professionalism for a project such as this. Not worth the detour unfortunately.
Very pleasant place, interesting exhibition which traces the past of the town of Châtillon and welcoming and attentive staff!
Well done to the friends of the old chatillon the conferences of Nov and Dec were great the place is ready for 2022 I hope it remains open
Absolutely worth discovering, managed by passionate volunteers
Very beautiful collections of local heritage
The history of our city and knowing the inhabitants
